304
00:24:10,319 --> 00:24:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] pitanja o Koreji.

305
00:24:11,079 --> 00:24:13,799
[SPEAKER_00] I on se otvori,

306
00:24:13,799 --> 00:24:15,240
[SPEAKER_00] dosta počnemo pričati o ratu,

307
00:24:15,240 --> 00:24:17,140
[SPEAKER_00] svemu što se događalo tamo,

308
00:24:17,140 --> 00:24:19,200
[SPEAKER_00] krajem 50. i početkom 60.

309
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] i njega iznenade što mi uopće znamo za tu situaciju.

310
00:24:23,019 --> 00:24:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] To je, za one koji ne znate,

311
00:24:25,099 --> 00:24:26,720
