318
00:24:38,819 --> 00:24:40,440
[SPEAKER_00] postoji jedan veliki zid.

319
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:41,700
[SPEAKER_00] Za njih deset godina,

320
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:43,720
[SPEAKER_00] 40.000 ljudi uspilo pobjeći

321
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:44,559
[SPEAKER_00] Sjeverne Koreje.

322
00:24:45,559 --> 00:24:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on tu iznosi svoju osobnu priču.

323
00:24:47,519 --> 00:24:49,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo priču nacije,

324
00:24:49,819 --> 00:24:50,779
[SPEAKER_00] nego kaže

325
00:24:50,779 --> 00:24:53,740
[SPEAKER_00] znam za 12 ljudi

326
00:24:53,740 --> 00:24:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] iz moje bliske obitelji

327
00:24:55,460 --> 00:24:57,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji su u trenutku primjere

328
00:24:57,420 --> 00:24:58,720
[SPEAKER_00] ostali s krive strane.

329
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, nikad ih nisam upoznao,

330
00:25:02,059 --> 00:25:03,940
[SPEAKER_00] a vjerojatno ih nikad neću ni upoznat.

331
00:25:03,940 --> 00:25:06,799
[SPEAKER_00] Počinju iznositi priče

332
00:25:06,799 --> 00:25:08,259
[SPEAKER_00] takvih obitelji

333
00:25:08,259 --> 00:25:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] koje su ostale podijeljene.

334
00:25:09,420 --> 00:25:11,279
[SPEAKER_00] Njegdje su čak obitelji,

335
00:25:11,279 --> 00:25:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] majka i otac obitelji

336
00:25:13,599 --> 00:25:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] ostali odvojeni

337
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:15,779
[SPEAKER_00] na različitim stranama.

338
00:25:15,779 --> 00:25:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] I to i danas traje.

339
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:19,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ti ljudi ne mogu se pomjeriti.

340
00:25:19,539 --> 00:25:21,819
[SPEAKER_00] Njihova nacija cijela je razdarana.

341
00:25:21,819 --> 00:25:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] Na pola.

342
00:25:23,480 --> 00:25:27,480
[SPEAKER_00] I kroz to mi slušamo

343
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:29,880
[SPEAKER_00] i on počinje nas onda ispitivati.

344
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:32,839
[SPEAKER_00] Jure kaže da je iz Bosne i Hercegovine.

345
00:25:32,839 --> 00:25:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] I on počinje,

346
00:25:34,980 --> 00:25:36,200
[SPEAKER_00] a kak je sad tamo stanje?

347
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] Mi njemu počnemo pričati.

348
00:25:37,960 --> 00:25:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] On je mislio da tamo cjetaju ruže,

349
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:41,559
