351
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:46,700
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo mi počeli objašnjavati

352
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] kakva je situacija trenutno u Bosni.

353
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo dan prije toga je

354
00:25:49,599 --> 00:25:52,700
[SPEAKER_00] bila izglasana ona rezolucija

355
00:25:52,700 --> 00:25:54,099
[SPEAKER_00] UN-u o Srebrenici,

356
00:25:54,099 --> 00:25:55,559
[SPEAKER_00] koja je još dodatno zakuhala

357
00:25:55,559 --> 00:25:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] cijelu situaciju koja je napeta

358
00:25:57,099 --> 00:25:59,079
[SPEAKER_00] između pogotovo

359
00:25:59,079 --> 00:26:00,799
[SPEAKER_00] Srba i Bošnjaka.

360
00:26:00,799 --> 00:26:02,019
[SPEAKER_00] Sad mi njemu objašnjavamo,

361
00:26:02,019 --> 00:26:04,819
[SPEAKER_00] objašnjavamo, to je objašnjavamo na način na koji djelujemo,

362
00:26:04,819 --> 00:26:06,759
[SPEAKER_00] tamo misijski, kroz misiju Mladi za mir.

363
00:26:06,759 --> 00:26:09,839
[SPEAKER_00] On se toliko oduševio da je sutra dan,

364
00:26:09,839 --> 00:26:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] nakon što je razgovarao sa svojim nadbiskupom,

365
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] došao i predložio nam da ko zajednica dođemo u Seul,

366
00:26:16,460 --> 00:26:17,900
[SPEAKER_00] kad bude 2027.

367
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] i da predstavimo misiju Mladi za mir.

368
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:23,660
[SPEAKER_00] Odnosno da predstavimo mladima koji žive

369
00:26:23,660 --> 00:26:25,640
[SPEAKER_00] u teškim situacijama,

370
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:27,559
[SPEAKER_00] u teškim zemljama gdje vladaju sukobi,

371
00:26:27,559 --> 00:26:29,359
[SPEAKER_00] gdje vladaju napetosti,

372
00:26:29,359 --> 00:26:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] kako djelovati, kako širiti evanđelje

373
00:26:31,299 --> 00:26:32,400
[SPEAKER_00] u takvim situacijama.

374
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:35,359
[SPEAKER_00] Kako biti svjetlo

375
00:26:35,359 --> 00:26:37,880
[SPEAKER_00] tamo gdje svi misle da je najbolje otiće.

376
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] I to se vjerojatno ne bi dogodilo

377
00:26:41,400 --> 00:26:42,839
[SPEAKER_00] da mi njemu prvo nismo pustili,

378
00:26:42,839 --> 00:26:44,259
[SPEAKER_00] da njega nismo saslušali.

379
00:26:44,259 --> 00:26:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] Jer se on uspio otvoriti na osobnoj rezini

380
00:26:46,980 --> 00:26:48,880
