436
00:29:10,299 --> 00:29:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] samom Kristu.

437
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:14,500
[SPEAKER_00] Tom Kristu koji želi ući u njegov život,

438
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:17,099
