439
00:29:17,099 --> 00:29:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji želi biti svjetlo u toj situaciji,

440
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] u toj obitelji, u svim tim problemima.

441
00:29:21,420 --> 00:29:22,859
[SPEAKER_00] On mu se otvara

442
00:29:22,859 --> 00:29:26,339
[SPEAKER_00] i naš posao završava u trenutku

443
00:29:26,339 --> 00:29:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] kad oni dođu do tog susreta s uskrslim.

444
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa u evanđelju?

445
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:40,140
[SPEAKER_00] Isus ostaje s njima tijekom večeri jer ih je zainteresirao.

446
00:29:40,140 --> 00:29:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] Oni uopće nisu znali u tom trenutku da je to još Krist.

447
00:29:42,779 --> 00:29:47,779
[SPEAKER_00] On njima navješta evanđelje, zašto je on trebao umrijeti po prorocima i po pismima.

448
00:29:48,359 --> 00:29:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] On još uvijek ne razumiju i na kraju ga prepoznaju u lomljenju kruha.

449
00:29:51,559 --> 00:29:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] U Euharistiji ga prepoznaju.

450
00:29:54,599 --> 00:29:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa kad svate, kad dođe spoznaja, on nestane.

451
00:29:59,940 --> 00:30:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ali njima to više nije ni bitno.

452
00:30:02,079 --> 00:30:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ih dovedemo do tog susreta,

453
00:30:05,579 --> 00:30:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad ih dovedemo do susreta sa živim Bogom,

454
00:30:08,119 --> 00:30:09,640
[SPEAKER_00] što je naš cilj,

455
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:11,700
[SPEAKER_00] ne navezati ljude na sebe,

456
00:30:11,700 --> 00:30:13,660
[SPEAKER_00] nego dovez ga do susreta sa živim Bogom,

457
00:30:13,660 --> 00:30:16,319
[SPEAKER_00] koji je taj koji rješava njihove probleme,

458
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:19,160
[SPEAKER_00] koji im daje utjehu i sve ono ostalo što im je potrebno,

459
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] mi tu više nismo toliko potrebni.

460
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo njih ispratili na putu

461
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,400
[SPEAKER_00] i šta onda oni rade?

462
00:30:25,400 --> 00:30:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] Oni postaju oni koji navještaju dalje.

463
00:30:28,140 --> 00:30:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su ti koji navještaju.

464
00:30:30,579 --> 00:30:31,660
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događa?

465
00:30:31,660 --> 00:30:34,299
[SPEAKER_00] Oni svačaju, ovo je bio Krist,

466
00:30:34,299 --> 00:30:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] više ne idu u Emmaus,

467
00:30:35,599 --> 00:30:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] nego se vraćaju Jeruzalem učenicima i govore,

468
00:30:37,619 --> 00:30:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] susreli smo Krista.

469
00:30:38,579 --> 00:30:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] I na taj način,

470
00:30:42,119 --> 00:30:43,640
[SPEAKER_00] ono što smo mi radili,

471
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:44,839
[SPEAKER_00] oni počinju raditi drugima.

472
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] Naš zadatak je ispratiti ljude

473
00:30:51,019 --> 00:30:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] u njihovim teškim situacijama,

474
00:30:54,619 --> 00:30:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] u njihovim beznađima,

475
00:30:56,079 --> 00:30:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] do toga da susretnu Krista.

476
00:30:59,319 --> 00:31:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] Papa kaže da je to najbolje u trenucima zajedništva.

477
00:31:02,720 --> 00:31:08,299
[SPEAKER_00] I zato su ovi susreti koje je Papa blagoslovio i potiče,

478
00:31:08,299 --> 00:31:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji se događaju nekad na međunarodnoj razini,

479
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,339
[SPEAKER_00] nekad se mogu događati na svjetskoj,

480
00:31:13,339 --> 00:31:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] nekad ovako na našoj maloj župnoj razini,

481
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:19,619
